title: Outdoor Basketball Court, Garages, Newly Renovated Interiors
posting_body: Pebble Cove Apartments in Renton, WA
Pebble Cove Apartments in Renton, WA, provides an unrivaled living experience.

All of our one, two and three bedroom homes are newly renovated and feature stainless steel appliances with white or espresso cabinetry, upgraded lighting, two-tone paint, and brushed nickel finishes for a sleek, modern look.
Our residents enjoy our unique floor plans with a kitchen pantry, walk-in closets, full size washer and dryers, and high-speed internet capability.
We offer covered parking and garages, a 24 hour fitness center, and a private patio or balcony with extra storage.
Located in the Fairwood area of Renton, you’ll find we offer a quality life-style at Pebble Cove that creates a living experience unequaled in the Renton Area.

We are only minutes from a variety of restaurants, licensed childcare centers, Cedar River Golf Course, Fairwood Shopping Center and Renton Landing, Westfield Mall, IKEA and other facilities to meet your daily needs.
We're also minutes away from multiple freeways and the airport for a quick commute!
Our community amenities sweeten the deal with both entertainment options and conveniences for your daily life.
Get to know Pebble Cove Apartments in Renton, WA.
We look forward to welcoming you home.
